  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. COU1 is the validation activity itself — the FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. This model has been applied in clinical research contexts to support regulatory submissions for Class II spinal implant systems, providing confidence in predicted construct stiffness and yield load under physiologically representative loading.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-compression-bending-adequacy",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/nagaraja-pedicle-screw-fea-ensemble",
